#Investigamos los Periodos que podemos detectar con esta curva de luz
print 'Minimo P:', times[1]-times[0], 'days'
print 'Maximo P:', times[-1]-times[0], 'days'
minP = 0.02
maxP = 30
resolution = 30000

Minimo P: 0.0203857421875 days
Maximo P: 33.0788574219 days
In [21]:
#Definimos los Periodos en un arreglo
periods = np.linspace(minP, maxP, resolution)
omega = 2 * np.pi / periods

Power = lomb_scargle(times, k2_var, np.ones(times.shape), omega, generalized=True)
P = (2*np.pi)/omega[np.argmax(Power)]
In [22]:
plt.figure(figsize=(7,6))

plt.subplot(211)
plt.plot((2*np.pi)/omega, Power)
plt.vlines(P, 0, 1, color='red', linestyles='--')
plt.xlabel('Periodos (dias)')
plt.ylabel('Power Spectrum')

plt.subplot(212)
plt.scatter(times/P %1, k2_var, color='b', marker='.', s=5)
plt.scatter((times/P %1)+1, k2_var, color='b', marker='.', s=5)
plt.xlabel('Phase')
plt.ylabel('Normalized flux')
plt.title('Primer Armonico: P = %2.3f dias' % P)

plt.tight_layout()
plt.savefig('P0.pdf', format='pdf')
In [23]:
def harmonic_model(x, c, a1, a2, a3, a4, a5, a6, \
                   A11, B11, A12, B12, A13, B13, A14, B14):
    return c + a1*Z[0] + a2*Z[1] + a3*Z[2] + a4*Z[3] + a5*Z[4] + a6*Z[5] \
    + A11*np.sin(1*2*np.pi*x/P) + B11*np.cos(1*2*np.pi*x/P) \
    + A12*np.sin(2*2*np.pi*x/P) + B12*np.cos(2*2*np.pi*x/P) \
    + A13*np.sin(3*2*np.pi*x/P) + B13*np.cos(3*2*np.pi*x/P) \
    + A14*np.sin(4*2*np.pi*x/P) + B14*np.cos(4*2*np.pi*x/P) \
In [24]:
popt, pcov = curve_fit(harmonic_model, times, k2_var)
In [25]:
residuos = k2_var-harmonic_model(times, *popt)
In [26]:
plt.figure(figsize=(8,6))

plt.subplot(211)
plt.plot(times-1900, k2_var, color='gray', alpha=0.8)
plt.plot(times-1900, harmonic_model(times, *popt), color='r', alpha=0.4)
plt.ylabel('Normalized flux', size=16)
plt.title(r'Fit para $N=4$ con un solo periodo ajustado')

plt.subplot(413)
plt.plot(times-1900, residuos, color='green', alpha=0.6)
plt.yticks(np.arange(-1., 1.5, 0.5))
plt.grid()
plt.xlabel('Time (BJD - 2456733)', size=14)
plt.ylabel('Residuos')

plt.savefig('R0.pdf', format='pdf')
print 'Residuos:', np.sum(residuos**2)

def harmonic_model2(x, c, a1, a2, a3, a4, a5, a6,\
                   A11, B11, A12, B12, A13, B13, A14, B14,\
                   A21, B21, A22, B22, A23, B23, A24, B24):
    return c + a1*Z[0] + a2*Z[1] + a3*Z[2] + a4*Z[3] + a5*Z[4] + a6*Z[5] \
    + A11*np.sin(1*2*np.pi*x/P) + B11*np.cos(1*2*np.pi*x/P) \
    + A12*np.sin(2*2*np.pi*x/P) + B12*np.cos(2*2*np.pi*x/P) \
    + A13*np.sin(3*2*np.pi*x/P) + B13*np.cos(3*2*np.pi*x/P) \
    + A14*np.sin(4*2*np.pi*x/P) + B14*np.cos(4*2*np.pi*x/P) \
    + A21*np.sin(1*2*np.pi*x/P1) + B21*np.cos(1*2*np.pi*x/P1) \
    + A22*np.sin(2*2*np.pi*x/P1) + B22*np.cos(2*2*np.pi*x/P1) \
    + A23*np.sin(3*2*np.pi*x/P1) + B23*np.cos(3*2*np.pi*x/P1) \
    + A24*np.sin(4*2*np.pi*x/P1) + B24*np.cos(4*2*np.pi*x/P1)

def harmonic_model3(x, c, a1, a2, a3, a4, a5, a6,\
                   A11, B11, A12, B12, A13, B13, A14, B14,\
                   A21, B21, A22, B22, A23, B23, A24, B24,\
                   A31, B31, A32, B32, A33, B33, A34, B34):
    return c + a1*Z[0] + a2*Z[1] + a3*Z[2] + a4*Z[3] + a5*Z[4] + a6*Z[5] \
    + A11*np.sin(1*2*np.pi*x/P) + B11*np.cos(1*2*np.pi*x/P) \
    + A12*np.sin(2*2*np.pi*x/P) + B12*np.cos(2*2*np.pi*x/P) \
    + A13*np.sin(3*2*np.pi*x/P) + B13*np.cos(3*2*np.pi*x/P) \
    + A14*np.sin(4*2*np.pi*x/P) + B14*np.cos(4*2*np.pi*x/P) \
    + A21*np.sin(1*2*np.pi*x/P1) + B21*np.cos(1*2*np.pi*x/P1) \
    + A22*np.sin(2*2*np.pi*x/P1) + B22*np.cos(2*2*np.pi*x/P1) \
    + A23*np.sin(3*2*np.pi*x/P1) + B23*np.cos(3*2*np.pi*x/P1) \
    + A24*np.sin(4*2*np.pi*x/P1) + B24*np.cos(4*2*np.pi*x/P1) \
    + A31*np.sin(1*2*np.pi*x/P2) + B31*np.cos(1*2*np.pi*x/P2) \
    + A32*np.sin(2*2*np.pi*x/P2) + B32*np.cos(2*2*np.pi*x/P2) \
    + A33*np.sin(3*2*np.pi*x/P2) + B33*np.cos(3*2*np.pi*x/P2) \
    + A34*np.sin(4*2*np.pi*x/P2) + B34*np.cos(4*2*np.pi*x/P2)

def harmonic_model4(x, c, a1, a2, a3, a4, a5, a6,\
                   A11, B11, A12, B12, A13, B13, A14, B14,\
                   A21, B21, A22, B22, A23, B23, A24, B24,\
                   A31, B31, A32, B32, A33, B33, A34, B34,\
                   A41, B41, A42, B42, A43, B43, A44, B44):
    return c + a1*Z[0] + a2*Z[1] + a3*Z[2] + a4*Z[3] + a5*Z[4] + a6*Z[5] \
    + A11*np.sin(1*2*np.pi*x/P) + B11*np.cos(1*2*np.pi*x/P) \
    + A12*np.sin(2*2*np.pi*x/P) + B12*np.cos(2*2*np.pi*x/P) \
    + A13*np.sin(3*2*np.pi*x/P) + B13*np.cos(3*2*np.pi*x/P) \
    + A14*np.sin(4*2*np.pi*x/P) + B14*np.cos(4*2*np.pi*x/P) \
    + A21*np.sin(1*2*np.pi*x/P1) + B21*np.cos(1*2*np.pi*x/P1) \
    + A22*np.sin(2*2*np.pi*x/P1) + B22*np.cos(2*2*np.pi*x/P1) \
    + A23*np.sin(3*2*np.pi*x/P1) + B23*np.cos(3*2*np.pi*x/P1) \
    + A24*np.sin(4*2*np.pi*x/P1) + B24*np.cos(4*2*np.pi*x/P1) \
    + A31*np.sin(1*2*np.pi*x/P2) + B31*np.cos(1*2*np.pi*x/P2) \
    + A32*np.sin(2*2*np.pi*x/P2) + B32*np.cos(2*2*np.pi*x/P2) \
    + A33*np.sin(3*2*np.pi*x/P2) + B33*np.cos(3*2*np.pi*x/P2) \
    + A34*np.sin(4*2*np.pi*x/P2) + B34*np.cos(4*2*np.pi*x/P2) \
    + A41*np.sin(1*2*np.pi*x/P3) + B41*np.cos(1*2*np.pi*x/P3) \
    + A42*np.sin(2*2*np.pi*x/P3) + B42*np.cos(2*2*np.pi*x/P3) \
    + A43*np.sin(3*2*np.pi*x/P3) + B43*np.cos(3*2*np.pi*x/P3) \
